<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Information about financial services such as bank accounts, debit or credit cards, insurance, personal pensions and annuities for UK residents, businesses, and people living in the EU, Norway, Liechtenstein or Iceland.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<h3 id="stay-up-to-date">Stay up to date</h3>

<p>This page tells you what to do if the UK leaves the EU without a deal.</p>

<p>It will be updated if anything changes, including if a deal is agreed.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/government/brexit">Sign up for email alerts</a> to get the latest information.</p>
</div>

